## ðŸ’» Key Technical Challenges

### 1. 15% Bundle Size Reduction (324KB â†’ 277KB)

<ImageDescription src="/images/camerafi-studio/optimization_chart.webp" alt="Bundle size reduction chart">
  Led the <strong>optimization of Webpack configurations</strong> to improve initial loading speed.
